title: American Academy of Ophthalmology 6-13 - Tenuki vol 1
description:
This are books 6-13 from the 6th edition of the American Academy of Ophthalmology.

This is the start of an ophthalmology collection, firstly started by Tenuki and with some additions from users all over the internet. In fact, it's a package extracted from a Facebook group which has recently become non-free.

For all the users who, as myself, joined the old Emedicina.biz. This is for you ;)

Content:
Section 5: Neuro-Ophthalmology 
Section 6: Pediatric Ophthalmology and Strabismus
Section 7: Orbit, Eyelids, and Lacrimal System
Section 8: External Disease and Cornea 
Section 9: Intraocular Inflammation and Uveitis
Section 10: Glaucoma
Section 11: Lens and Cataract
Section 12: Retina and Vitreous
Section 13: Refractive Surgery


Sharing speed will be low during the first days. Be patient
